{"tid":1008684,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"tg新型賣料狗，錢嘉樂","createTime":"2019-02-04T16:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T17:20:49.000Z","uid":120896,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"99172ad0223ba26bd594499ee64a7f5b56ae3941","tid":1008684,"uid":120896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:09:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/nomoneynohappy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnomoneynohappy&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ6Zg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=d2b935db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nomoneynohappy</a><br />\n<br />\n臨近新年，相信好多手足都特別需要金錢，又或者想新年新開始贏大錢，有啲不法之徒就乘虛而入，做賣料狗呃人，近期tg就出現左一位新賣料狗-錢嘉樂<br />\n<br />\n詳情自己入去睇，大概係佢自相矛盾之類既對話，希望咁多位手足唔好誤墮陷阱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外小妹亦都有自己青盧，出下心水，撚下啲賣料狗咁，謝各位手足多多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新年快樂#adore<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/missapinkweeklytipsrecord\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmissapinkweeklytipsrecord&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ6Zg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=71602d0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/missapinkweeklytipsrecord</a>"},{"pid":"383a1c065729d7cf92f3a1edbdb80696a06608ad","tid":1008684,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:17:24.000Z","msg":"爭生意?"},{"pid":"b5281723c4a209ac8c03b79ca3e29d149f1bc2f1","tid":1008684,"uid":120896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"383a1c065729d7cf92f3a1edbdb80696a06608ad","tid":1008684,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:17:24.000Z","msg":"爭生意?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:19:04.000Z","msg":"從來冇收過錢賣料，純粹睇唔過眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab67189d33235bc9dc50b36fc4e4b2717f59f1da","tid":1008684,"uid":2313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot